&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a Lifecycle Marketing Manager to own the end-to-end user journey for Aiven&#39;s self-serve customer base. This role is deeply focused on what happens after someone signs up — turning new users into activated ones, activated users into paying customers, and paying customers into expanded accounts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll combine segmentation, behavioural data, and personalised messaging to build a lifecycle program that drives measurable monetisation outcomes. This includes everything from in-console nudges to nurture flows to expansion signals.&lt;/p&gt;
